  "prompt": "What are the best 17.3 inch laptop bags?",
  "response": "When looking for the best 17.3 inch laptop bags, it's important to consider factors like protection, functionality, and style. Here are some popular and highly-rated options for you to consider:\n\n1. **Everki Business 120 Travel-Friendly Laptop Backpack**: Known for its high quality and ample storage space, this backpack ensures your laptop is well-protected while providing various compartments for your other belongings.\n\n2. **Targus Drifter II Backpack**: This bag offers rugged construction, multiple compartments, and a padded laptop section. It's great for travelers or students who need to carry a laptop and other essentials.\n\n3. **eBags Professional Slim Laptop Backpack**: With a sleek and professional design, this backpack offers organized storage pockets and dedicated space for a 17.3 inch laptop.\n\n4. **Samsonite Tectonic Lifestyle Easy Rider Laptop Backpack**: Offers robust protection and a durable design with ergonomic straps for comfortable carrying.\n\n5. **SwissGear 5358 USB ScanSmart Laptop Backpack**: Known for its quality and innovative design, it's equipped with a USB port for charging devices, and has a protective laptop section.\n\n6. **Case Logic DLBP-116 Laptop Backpack**: This sleek, urban backpack provides ample space for a 17.3 inch laptop and is designed for daily commutes or travel.\n\n7. **KROSER Travel Laptop Backpack**: This budget-friendly option provides extensive compartments, including a padded laptop section and a USB port.\n\n8. **Timbuk2 Authority Laptop Backpack**: Known for its sturdy design and practical compartments, this backpack is ideal for professional use.\n\n9. **HP 17.3 Laptop Case**: A straightforward and padded case designed specifically for a 17.3 inch laptop, ensuring protection and easy mobility.\n\n10. **AmazonBasics Laptop Backpack**: Cost-effective and capable, this backpack offers multiple compartments and padded protection for your laptop.\n\n11. **Osprey Packs Apogee Laptop Backpack**: Popular for its ergonomic design and durability, this backpack includes a padded laptop sleeve and convenient organizational pockets.\n\n12. **Lenovo Legion Recon Gaming Backpack**: Tailored for gamers, this backpack provides ample space and protection for a 17.3 inch laptop and gaming accessories.\n\n13. **Solo New York Bryant Rolling Laptop Bag**: A rolling bag option that is great for travel, offering dedicated compartments for a laptop and other essentials.\n\n14. **Victorinox Altmont Professional Fliptop Laptop Backpack**: Features a sleek design and organized compartments, ideal for professional environments.\n\n15. **Dakine Campus Backpack**: Known for its durability and spacious compartments, it\u2019s ideal for students who need to carry a laptop along with textbooks and other gear.\n\n16. **Kenneth Cole Reaction Polyester Dual Compartment Laptop Business Backpack**: Offers stylish functionality and durable construction with multiple compartments for business use.\n\n17. **Pacsafe Metrosafe LS450 Anti-Theft Backpack**: Provides security with anti-theft features and padded protection for a laptop, ideal for travel.\n\nWhen choosing a laptop bag, ensure it fits your lifestyle and specific needs, whether it's additional compartments, ergonomic design, or security features.",
